description:
Data generated from the quantitative literature review "Quantifying uncertainty in forecasts of when and where invasions happen" (citation pending). 
 Code to produce publication figures is provided in figure_code.ipynb. 
 The data folder includes two datasets: evaluation_matrix.csv, and detailed_uncertainty.csv, which correspond to the two data producing steps of the review process.&nbsp; &nbsp;

